    <h2>🚀 Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe in leveraging **Artificial Intelligence** to make knowledge accessible and easy to digest. Our mission is to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>✔️ **Simplify information processing with AI-powered summarization**</li>
