    <h2>💡 Why This Project?</h2>
    <p>Information overload is a real problem. Whether it's **research papers, articles, or historical studies**, reading lengthy content can be time-consuming. **Summarize AI** was created to solve this problem using advanced **AI & NLP** techniques to generate quick, precise, and easy-to-read summaries.</p>

    <h2>🛠 How It Works</h2>
    <p>Our system follows a **3-step approach** to deliver high-quality results:</p>

    <h3>🔍 Step 1: Extracting Data</h3>
    <p>We scrape **credible sources** to gather the latest and most accurate information about a given topic.</p>

    <h3>🤖 Step 2: AI Summarization</h3>
    <p>Using **Python's Sumy library**, we analyze and summarize the text, ensuring key information is retained.</p>

    <h3>🗺️ Step 3: Creating a Mind Map</h3>
    <p>With **Graphviz**, we generate a **visual representation** of the summarized content, making it easier to understand complex relationships.</p>

